Welcome to the newly upgraded world!  This update was long overdue.  Before I had to manually add avatar pedestals for each new vatar I found and update the world, and it was such a pain I stopped doing it at all in mid 2025.  NOW though the avatars are pulled from a list hosted on github, and so now to add avatars all I need to do is update the list!  So much simpler and easier!
.
If avatars are not loading at all even after 60 seconds, make sure "Allow Untrusted URL's" is turned on in your vrchat settings.
.
Total Number of Avatars: 900+
